Function for hide a part of text and show it after click on href
(Depends on jQuery library)

hidden_text(el, len);
el - DOM element, target text container
len - number of chars to hide

EXAMPLE:

<div class="more">1 (234) 567-89-123</div>
<script> hidden_text( $('.more'), 15 ); </script>
--------------------------------------------------
Before click: 1 (234) 567-89-...
After click:  1 (234) 567-89-123
